fields.search:
with table_plain as (SELECT artist_lastfm, listeners_lastfm, tag_lastfm
FROM artists.artists lateral view explode(split(tags_lastfm,';')) tags_lastfm AS tag_lastfm)

SELECT artist_lastfm, sum(listeners_lastfm) as sl
FROM table_plain tb1
inner JOIN (select tag_lastfm, sum(listeners_lastfm) as s from table_plain GROUP BY
tag_lastfm ORDER BY s DESC LIMIT 10 ) tb2
ON tb1.tag_lastfm = tb2.tag_lastfm
GROUP BY tb1.artist_lastfm 
ORDER BY sl DESC 
limit 10
